  "3072760": {
    "name": "Retro Relics",
    "steam_appid": 3072760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>文物寻宝家是</strong>一款故事驱动的休闲沙盒类寻宝游戏。在游戏里你可以沉浸在大自然中，用手中的金属探测器寻找古代文物。探索、挖掘、帮助其他人找到丢失的物品，并集齐硬币和文物藏品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/fb5c37ff90d349cc13f2d194942c63e3.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探测并找到古代文物</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助金属探测器，你可以挖掘到各个时代的文物，如硬币、纽扣、带扣、珠宝、武器装备、宗教文物等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/00292253398a38680804e8a874a39556.poster.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/00292253398a38680804e8a874a39556.webm?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/00292253398a38680804e8a874a39556.mp4?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/c42cb95c51af3a91aa823eb0d48b27c7.poster.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/c42cb95c51af3a91aa823eb0d48b27c7.webm?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/c42cb95c51af3a91aa823eb0d48b27c7.mp4?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/c53e9b403e9e4c503c41a218fdbcd32d.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索自然，在旅途中放松身心</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开古代遗迹的神秘面纱，你可以探索茂密的森林、尘土飞扬的田野，还可以在海滩上寻宝时顺带放松身心！在冒险的途中，还能看到许多动物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/72b5acc9f39e2b9c59be223eac3b89e0.avif?t=1767807975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras_big/72b5acc9f39e2b9c59be223eac3b89e0.avif?t=1767807975 width=1170 height=658 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/94cd0c0d2967bd0e10e1bb14826cdb03.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>帮助他人寻回丢失的物品</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助镇上的居民寻回物品，包括伤心的狗主人、奇怪的猎人和一位试图破译古代废墟秘密的博学考古学家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/1097bab360bede9f86330a0556e941bc.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>集齐硬币和文物藏品</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集一百多种不同文物，并放在你舒适的家园中展示。从现代垃圾到古代黄金遗物，你可以寻找一百多种手绘的像素文物，并从中选出最珍贵和漂亮的藏品来装饰你的私人博物馆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/639e77c345d510651847ce26fdd5faba.avif?t=1767807975\" width=366 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/e512c1bf2db8a8101f3b3c5a39af8949.avif?t=1767807975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras_big/e512c1bf2db8a8101f3b3c5a39af8949.avif?t=1767807975 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/752b889fcc889b17e0d5d39b589478f4.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>清理自然环境并帮助动物</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流到自然界的可不仅仅只有宝藏——捡起垃圾，保护环境，让动物都能回到自己的家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/527d37dde783dedd042d0ef5be4323e0.poster.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/527d37dde783dedd042d0ef5be4323e0.webm?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/527d37dde783dedd042d0ef5be4323e0.mp4?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/51909807264b825741827c3f513dbb13.avif?t=1767807975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras_big/51909807264b825741827c3f513dbb13.avif?t=1767807975 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/21bf27b1bfa4252cfc0a0385cdffe4fa.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为下一次的寻宝之旅整装待发</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在家园中你可以出售文物、通过电子邮件承接新任务、管理藏品以及升级装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/08e191fc096f736e56e19cda6b803a8f.poster.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/08e191fc096f736e56e19cda6b803a8f.webm?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/08e191fc096f736e56e19cda6b803a8f.mp4?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于我：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 我叫Jonas，今年31岁，来自德国。我一个人利用空余时间开发文物寻宝家。 我自身是一名狂热的金属探测爱好者，有多年的探测经验。游戏中你可以发掘的物品里面有很多都是我亲自找到的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/159146be1d7f4fa9cea01a5e56ea4c5b.poster.avif?t=1767807975\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/159146be1d7f4fa9cea01a5e56ea4c5b.webm?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/159146be1d7f4fa9cea01a5e56ea4c5b.mp4?t=1767807975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入群组</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你想参与到文物寻宝家的开发中来，或是提供反馈和建议，欢迎你加入我的Discord群组</p>",
